com.here.android.mpa.urbanmobility

Class ParkAndRideRouteOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.urbanmobility.ParkAndRideRouteOptions

  • public class ParkAndRideRouteOptions
extends java.lang.Object
    Options for Park And Ride mode, in which route calculation is optimized by switching from car to public transport

    IMPORTANT: Park And Ride routing is a Beta feature. The related classes are subject to change without notice.

    Audience:
    internal
